headline: Spotting Winners: Dayforce (NYSE:DAY) And HR Software Stocks In Q1
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how HR software stocks fared in Q1, starting with Dayforce (NYSE:DAY).
